==== Show vehicle speed in status bar ====
{{en/Feature|Old|align="right"|text=(since 0.2.0)}}
Whether or not the vehicle [[Main/en/show vehicle speed|speed is shown]] in the vehicle window status bar, where you can stop or start a train.
:''Possible Settings:'' <span style="color:green">'''On'''</span> or <span style="color:red">'''Off'''</span>
:''In [[Main/en/openttd.cfg]] config file:'' (vehicle_speed = <true|false>)
{{en/-}}
==== Allow building on slopes an coasts ====
{{en/Feature|Old|align="right"|text=(since 0.2.0)}}
Normally you can only [[Main/en/build on slopes|build tracks and roads on slopes]] parallel to the incline, with this patch you can build nearly everything on a slope because foundations will be built under it.
:''Possible Settings:'' <span style="color:green">'''On'''</span> or <span style="color:red">'''Off'''</span>
:''In Openttd.cfg config file:'' (build_on_slopes = <true|false>)
{{en/-}}
==== Enable building very long trains ====
{{en/Feature|Old|align="right"|text=(since 0.2.0)}}
You can build extremely long trains, aka [[Main/en/mammoth trains]].
:''Possible Settings:'' <span style="color:green">'''On'''</span> or <span style="color:red">'''Off'''</span>
:''In Openttd.cfg config file:'' (mammoth_trains = <true|false>)
{{en/-}}
==== Join train stations built next to each other ====
{{en/Feature|Old|align="right"|text=(since 0.2.0)}}
Stations built next to each other will be [[Main/en/join train stations|joined]] as long as the station spread is not too high.
:''Possible Settings:'' <span style="color:green">'''On'''</span> or <span style="color:red">'''Off'''</span>
:''In [[Main/en/Openttd.cfg]] config file:'' (join_stations = <true|false>)
{{en/-}}
==== Leave station when any cargo is full, if 'full load' ====
{{en/Feature|-0.6|align="right"|text=(since 0.2.0 to 0.6.3)}}
When this patch is enabled the vehicle will leave when [[Main/en/full load any cargo|any cargo is fully loaded]]. If you use lots of planes to transport passengers and mail you may want to disable this patch.
:''Possible Settings:'' <span style="color:green">'''On'''</span> or <span style="color:red">'''Off'''</span>
:''In [[Main/en/Openttd.cfg]] config file:'' (full_load_any = <true|false>)
{{en/-}
==== Turn off inflation ====
{{en/Feature|-Old|align="right"|text=(since 0.2.0 to 0.3.3)}}
Whether [[Main/en/disable inflation|turn off inflation is on or off]], if it is on the prices of things will increase as you progress. This option has been renamed to [[Main/en/#Inflation|Inflation]] in 0.3.4.
:''Possible Settings:'' <span style="color:red">'''0%'''</span> to <span style="color:#00693E">'''100%'''</span>
:''In [[Main/en/Openttd.cfg]] config file:'' (noinflation = <true|false>)
{{en/-}}
